    <item>
      <title>世界上规模最大的选举是对莫迪对印度控制力的考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-18/a-guide-to-india-s-six-week-election-that-will-test-modi-s-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近十亿人将前往世界上最大的民主国家投票，那里蓬勃发展的经济可能有利于总理及其执政的印度人民党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-04-18/a-guide-to-india-s-six-week-election-that-will-test-modi-s-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:31:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rishi Sunak 计划审核病假条以解决不活动问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/rishi-sunak-plans-uk-sick-note-review-in-push-to-tackle-inactivity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 正计划审查英国的病假单系统，此举旨在解决英国 20 世纪 90 年代以来与健康相关的不活动现象持续时间最长的持续上升趋势，从而推动经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/rishi-sunak-plans-uk-sick-note-review-in-push-to-tackle-inactivity</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度大规模选举拉开帷幕，莫迪押注第三任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/india-elections-day-1-voting-in-world-s-largest-democracy-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近10亿印度人周五开始在持续六周多的选举中投票，权衡是否给予总理纳伦德拉·莫迪第三个五年任期，以继续其经济和印度教民族主义政策的混合政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/india-elections-day-1-voting-in-world-s-largest-democracy-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国否决联合国让巴勒斯坦成为世界机构正式成员的申请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/us-vetoes-un-bid-to-make-palestine-full-un-member</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国否决了巴勒斯坦成为联合国正式会员国的申请，拒绝了巴勒斯坦争取更广泛国际认可的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/us-vetoes-un-bid-to-make-palestine-full-un-member</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 21:19:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普封口费案中陪审团的选择需要了解什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/all-12-jurors-chosen-in-trump-hush-money-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 在纽约举行的首次刑事审判已选出 12 名陪审员和一名候补陪审员，这位前总统被指控在 2016 年大选前伪造商业记录以掩盖性丑闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/all-12-jurors-chosen-in-trump-hush-money-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:41:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗告诉联合国，如果以色列停止“冒险主义”，伊朗准备降级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-ready-to-de-escalate-if-israel-stops-adventurism-un-told</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗外交部长侯赛因·阿米拉卜杜拉希安在联合国表示，只要伊朗同意停止针对德黑兰利益的进一步军事行动，伊朗准备缓和与以色列的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-ready-to-de-escalate-if-israel-stops-adventurism-un-told</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 18:20:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
